

**Haꞌichu wepogida ab ha amjed g uhdwis oidag chikpandam **

1 “Id ant am wo em‑tashogi id hekaj mant wo haꞌichu wepogi g Jiosh kownaltalig. Heg o wepogidas mat g uhdwis oidag enigakam wabsh i siꞌalim am him k haꞌi ha ui g oꞌodham mat am wo chikp oidaj ed. 2 T g ha‑namkidadag d wo hegaik mo haschu i uꞌu g pion tash ab. T am ha hekaj hihim k chikp. 

3 “T am hahawa ep hih humukt ohla ch ed. K am haꞌi gegok g oꞌodham ch pi haꞌichu has wua. 4 K hab ha ahg, ‘Nt wo s‑ap em‑namkid mamt wo chikp am ni‑oidag ed.’ 5 Kut wa woho am chikpano idam. T hab wa masma hab ep e juh am i gamai gohk ohla ch ed ch waik ohla ch ed. 

6 “K am hu d i hetasp ohla. T am hih kahya wui. K am wabsh haꞌi gegok. K hab kaij ab ha wui, ‘Shahchu am ahgch wabsh heki wua g tash pi haꞌichu has wuadch?’ 

7 “K hab kaij idam, ‘Pi at hedai t‑chikpanach.’ 

“K hab hahawa ep kaij ab ha wui, ‘Pegih, k am wo hihim k wo chikp am ni‑oidag ed.’ 

8 “Neh, t gam hu si i juh. Kut ihda oidag enigakam hab ah g e‑pionag ha‑geꞌejig, ‘Ab g i ha waid g pion k ab wo i ha namkidahi. T hegam wehpeg wo e namkid mant si ha oidch an ha ui k amjed hegam ehp mant ep ha ui k hegam ga hu si ha oidk wo e namkid mant si wehpeg an ha ui.’ 

9 “Kut hegam mat gam hu si i juhk chikp mo d i hetasp ohla ab ui g e‑namkidadag haꞌakia mo heꞌekia uꞌu g pion tash ab ch amjed wehs g haꞌi. 

10 “Kut ab ha ai hegam mat wabsh i siꞌalim chikp. K hab e ahg mat baꞌich i muꞌi wo ui g e‑namkidadag. Mt wabshaba haꞌakia wa ha namkid. 11 T ab ui g e‑lialiga k babgat ab wui g e‑ahmo k ab wui hab kaij, 12 ‘Neh, hegam oꞌodham mapt si oidk an ha ui al hemako ohla ab chikp. Kutt ahchim ge tash oidk chikp am s‑toni k ed. Kupt eda am wo haꞌakia t‑namkid mapt hegam.’ 

13 “K hab kaij g oidag enigakam ab wui hegai mo ha wehhejed neok, ‘Neh, ni‑nawoj, pi ant shaꞌi em‑iattogi namt pi am wa apꞌech mamt haꞌakia k ab wo chikp ni‑wehhejed. 14 Pegih, ab g wabsh wo uhꞌi g e‑namkidadag k gam hu hihim uhpam no hig pi ab ni‑ab ahni hejel mant haꞌakia wo wa ha namkid hegam mant gam hu si i juhk ha ui mant ahpim heꞌekia em‑namkid. 15 Ab o ni‑ab mant has masma wo hekaj g ni‑lialiga. Aha nam wabsh s‑ni‑hehgamk mani s‑hemajima?’ ” 

16 D hab hahawa ep kaij g Jesus, “Nehꞌe, t hekaj hab hegam mo gam hu si i ha oidch d wo wehpegkamk ch hegam mo d wehpegkam ga hu wo si ha oidchk.” 

**Mash g Jesus idani waikko am ahg g e‑muhkig **

*An g neid g Mark 10:32-34; Luke 18:31-34 *

17 Am achd i t‑nakog k gam hu hihi. Kud g Jesus am hejelko t‑wai ahchim gamai gohk 18 k hab kaij, “Neh, am att wo hihi Jerusalem wui. T hegam mo s‑ni‑kehꞌid am wo ni‑dagito ha wui g uꞌugchu papal ch chehanig em‑mashchamdam. Kut idam ab wo haꞌichu ni‑abch s‑ni‑muꞌamk 19 k am wo ni‑dagito ha wui g goꞌol hemajkam. T idam wo nahnko ni‑ahgad ch wo ni‑gewittan k amjed ab wo ni‑sisish kots t ab. Nt ab wo muh. T am wo him k d wo i waik tashk amjed. Nt ab wo uhpam i wuhsh muhkig amjed.” 

**Mash g James ch John chum si e haꞌichuchud **

*An g neid g Mark 10:25-45 *

20 D eda am t‑wehmaj g ha‑jeꞌe g James ch John. D idam am wehmaj hihi Jesus wui ab haꞌichu s‑tahnimk. D g ha‑jeꞌe ab si has elid k ab wui hab kaij matsh ab wo haꞌichu tai. 

21 D hab kaij g Jesus, “Shahchu ap tatchua?” 

D hab kaij ihda, “Pt hig wo i ha chuhcha idam gohk ni‑mahmad mat am m‑oidch d wo hahaꞌichuk mapt hekid am wo i himch g e‑kownaltalig.” 

22 D hab kaij g Jesus ab ha wui, “Pi am shaꞌi ap mahch mam haschu ab ni‑tahni. Wehpeg ant ab wo nako g geꞌe shoꞌigdag. Kut hegam mat am ni‑oidch d wo si hahaꞌichuk hab waꞌap wo e juh.” 

D hab kaij idam, “Pegih, tt wo t‑nako.” 

23 D hab hahawa ha ahg g Jesus, “Pegih, woho amt ab wo nako hegai hab mahs shoꞌigdag. K wabshaba pi ab hu ni‑ab manis ahni am wo i ha chuhcha mat hedai am ni‑oidch d wo hahaꞌichuk. Hegam at am wo i e chuhcha mat hedai i ha wehhejed am apꞌech g Jiosh.” 

24 Kuchd ahchim haꞌi babgat ab ha wui hegam gohk mad hab masma ab hejel chum e haꞌichuchud. 25 D g Jesus ab hahawa wehs i t‑hemapad k hab kaij ab t‑wui, “S‑mahch am mo g ha‑maliomig s‑gewkam ha chehani g e‑pionag ch g ha wanimeddam am ha himchudahim. 26-27 T wabshaba pi hab masma hab wo shaꞌi chum mahsk am em‑shahgid. Mt wabsh si s‑hemajim am wo i ha wehmtad g e‑wehm wohochuddam hab sha masma mam d wabsh ha‑pionag mamtp wo tatchuad mamt wo ha wanimedad. 28 Ahni ani hab wa masma si s‑hemajim i em‑wehmt ch pi ab hu ni‑haꞌichuchud em‑dahm, chum anis d Jiosh si Kehsha. Ab o em‑wui him g s‑koꞌok namkidadag heg hekaj pi ap em‑chuꞌijig. Nt wabshaba ahni em‑wehhejed wo nako mamt wo e wupulꞌo.” Neh, bad kaij g Jesus. 

**Matsh g Jesus ha doaj g gohk pi neneadam **

*An g neid g Mark 10:46-52; Luke 18:35-43 *

29 Kuchd gam hu i wuwha ab Jerico t amjed. D muꞌi hemajkam ab i t‑oi. 30 D am hu hebai wohg hugid an gohk am dadha g pi neneadam oꞌodham. Kuchd am hihim. D am i t‑kah k s‑mai mo an him g Jesus k si s‑kaidam hab chechꞌe, “Ab g si i s‑t‑hoꞌigeꞌid, ahpi map d s‑apꞌekam t‑kownalig ch apsh d t‑kownaligbad David amjedkam.” 

31 D hegam mo an ha wehgaj si s‑ha kehꞌid ch hab ha ahg mat wo pi shahmunik. 

D wabshaba baꞌich haha wabsh i s‑kaidam hab kaij, “Ab g si i s‑t‑hoꞌigeꞌid, ahpi Davidbad amjedkam.” 

32 Kud am hahawa i kekiwua g Jesus k ab i ha waid k hab kaij, “Shahchu am tatchua mant hab wo em‑juni?” 

33 D hab kaij idam, “Si g s‑t‑hoꞌigeꞌid k ab i t‑nenchud.” 

34 Kud si s‑ha hoꞌigeꞌel g Jesus k ab ha taht ha‑wuhpui ab. D ha hekaj haꞌichu s‑ap neid k ab i oi. 

